== Books ==
[[Asiatic Society of Bangladesh]] published his book ''History of Bangladesh'' where he explored the historical and social emergences of Bangladesh as well as the growth of Islam in the country. In his economy related book "Porarthoporotar Orthoniti" (tr. Otherminding Economics), he expressed the complex aspects of Economics in the lucid, unorthodox style [[J. K. Galbraith]].<ref name=Akbar/>

